Actions.Text: REFERRED TO COMMERCE, ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT AND SMALL BUSINESS

Title: Increases the number of package store licenses able to be held by one person
Summary: Increases the number of package store licenses able to be held by one person to two; permits certain licensees to buy and sell from other certain licensees.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to increasing the number of package store licenses able to be held by one person
